data.title: S kým spolupracujeme
data.meta_description: Dárci se u nás mohou vzdát finanční náhrady za odběr a věnovat ji na dobré účely. Stačí náhradu vhodit do kasičky na recepci.
data.text:
We help others

Some of our donors prefer to waive financial compensation and treat their donation as charity. It’s possible to drop the financial compensation into the moneybox at reception, and thus give help twice.

Cookie files will ensure better services

By clicking on “Accept all”, you agree with our website using cookie files, which allows us to provide you with the most relevant experience, as we will remember your preferences and repeated visits. You can manage your consent in the “Settings of cookie files” section. Please read our Cookies Policy.
